name: Terple
description: Terple is a slightly indica dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Tropicana Cookies X Slurricane #7 strains. This well-balanced bud packs the best of both its sativa and indica heritages, with full-bodied effects that will have you feeling fine for hours on end. Terple is often chosen to treat those suffering from conditions such as chronic pain, appetite loss or nausea, depression and chronic stress.
